== Overview ==
Scaven Grenadiers are aggressive frontline units used by the [[Scaven]] faction. With high payload and multiple weapon slots, they are built for explosive offense.

== Equipment ==
<gallery widths="100">
File:Handgrenades.jpg|link=Hand Grenades|[[Hand Grenades|Weapon: Hand Grenades]]
File:Submachinegun.jpg|link=Sub-Machine Gun|[[Sub-Machine Gun|Weapon: Sub-Machine Gun]]
</gallery>

== Faction ==
[[Scaven]]

== Location ==
Scaven Grenadiers may appear as hired support by completing a mission for any [[Scaven Settlement]] in [[Scaven Territory]] in [[Vulcore]].

== Combat Strategy ==
Use Scaven Grenadiers to saturate enemies with grenades and gunfire. Their lack of shielding is compensated by raw offense. Ideal when protected by shielded allies or during ambushes.

